1. Purpose

A coupled scalar wave toy evolved using Implicit-Explicit (IMEX) integrators and the CarpetX driver, using CPU kernels.

More info: https://github.com/annamalai-ps/IMEX/tree/main/IMEX_1D_scalar_wave_evolution